  "title": "Shuttle Bus Captain (Class 4+BDVL) 23 Seater - Mon to Fri",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>• Provide safe, smooth and pleasant bus journeys for passengers</p>\n<p>• Maintain cleanliness of the bus at all time</p>\n<p>• Adhere to all Malaysia and Singapore driving regulations.</p>\n<p>• Ensure all travel documents and permit are current and valid</p>\n<p>• Provide courteous and good services to all passengers and customers</p>\n<p>• Perform other related duties that may be assigned from time to time</p>\n<p>• Follow proper safety guideline and represent the company in a professional manner</p>\n<p>• Ability to work flexible hours, including weekends and public holiday</p>\n<p>• Ensure the comprehensive maintenance is carried out according to main schedule</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>• Obtain Singapore Class 4 driving licence</p>\n<p>• Possess at least 3 years of relevant experience</p>\n<p>• LTA Bus Vocational Licence is an advantage</p>\n<p>• Responsible and have good time management skills</p>\n<p>• Have good work conduct</p>\n<p>• Hardworking and good working attitude</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p>• Annual Leave 7 – 14 days</p>\n<p>• Birthday Token</p>\n<p>• Medical and Dental/Optical Claims</p>\n<p>• Quarterly and Yearly Performance Bonuses</p>\n<p>• Referral &amp; Long service awards</p>",
